                    <h2>Downloads Only $2.99</h2> 
                  </li> 
                  <li>Subscribe and save a buck each time you download a full one-hour class. That’s 25% savings with a monthly or prepaid membership.</li> 
                </ul> 
                <ul style="margin-bottom:25px;"> 
                  <li> 
                    <h5>All paid memberships</h5> 
                    <h2>Ambassador ID trial offer</h2> 
                  </li> 
